				}
			}]
		}
		{
			x: 3.5d
			y: -3.0d
			shape: "gear"
			subtitle: "Colection, collection, colllectionnnn! Left Click for more info"
			description: [
				"The Bee Box can be used to store up to 10 bees at a time. This box can also be used to collect the bees inside a next/hive. To do so, you'll have to smoke the hive/nest first with a Smoker. Shift Right-Click the hive/nest with the box to get the bees."
				""
				"To release your bees, just Shift Right-Click the box on a random block."
			]
			dependencies: ["36121AB6BF73E832"]
			id: "03EBA15C665809F7"
			tasks: [{
				id: "2B3B6BDC06427202"
				type: "item"
				item: "resourcefulbees:bee_box"
			}]
		}
		{
			title: "Waxed Planks"
			x: 3.5d
			y: -1.5d
			subtitle: "Fireproof and beautiful: The Waxed Planks are a nice building block. Additionally, these blocks are fireproof"
