			subtitle: "Electricity everywhere! Left Click for more info"
			description: ["The Centrifuge will use RF to turn your combs into resources. There is a limitation that it can only process honeycombs, not blocks. This process can be automated with Hoppers. Also, keep in mind that this Centrifuge will NOT allow you to process Honeycombs without bottles inside."]
