				type: "item"
				item: "resourcefulbees:t2_apiary"
			}]
		}
		{
			title: "Apiary Storage (3rd Age)"
			x: 14.5d
			y: -1.5d
			subtitle: "The Storage is the block where all the Apiary outputs will go. You can auto-export items from the Storage with hoopers or other pipes. Also, the storage can be upgraded with one out of 4 tiers. When honeycombs are produced by the bees, they will show up in the Apiary Storage, which can then be removed Manually, or automated via Hoppers or pipes from other mods"
			dependencies: ["7EF155944458998F"]
			id: "7FE3E70663C06FD8"
			tasks: [{
				id: "058C48142275CBBB"
				type: "item"
				item: "resourcefulbees:apiary_storage"
			}]
		}
		{
			title: "Apiary Breeder (3rd Age)"
			x: 13.0d
			y: -1.5d
			subtitle: "The Breeder is an optinal addition to the Apiary Multiblock. It will make breeding easier by allowing you to place the two bees, together with their food and a jar, inside it and not have the hassle of running around after them. If the breeding is successful, the new bee will be placed in the Apiary Storage"
			dependencies: ["7EF155944458998F"]
			id: "26695BDA9946F06F"
			tasks: [{
				id: "5370C6253BB7F5B6"
				type: "item"
